headline: Can Kim Hourihan’s Appointment Steer Realty Income (O) Toward Stronger Global Diversification?
summary: On October 14, 2025, Realty Income Corporation announced the appointment of Kim Hourihan, an accomplished global real estate executive at Invesco Real Estate, to its Board of Directors, and declared its 664th consecutive monthly dividend of $0.2695 per share, payable November 14, 2025. With Ms. Hourihan’s extensive experience in both US and international property markets, her addition is expected to strengthen Realty Income’s global expansion and governance as the company continues its track...
